{"tid":691252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯反擊︰不如話我滴汗搞到費明奴冷親！","createTime":"2018-06-05T14:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T19:26:42.000Z","uid":4661,"like":69,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc40033aa8c4e5e070e3a03847e288c07d6e9ff","tid":691252,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soccer.nbcsports.com/2018/06/05/sergio-ramos-hits-out-after-salah-karius-injury-fury/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.nbcsports.com%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2Fsergio-ramos-hits-out-after-salah-karius-injury-fury%2F&d=mbGP7JXlvFSBBMzyTBH6yDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bf85b984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soccer.nbcsports.com/2018/06/05/sergio-ramos-hits-out-after-salah-karius-injury-fury/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/ramos-karius.png?w=748&amp;h=432&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F05%2Framos-karius.png%3Fw%3D748%26h%3D432%26crop%3D1&h=e856c3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSergio Ramos hits out after Salah, Karius injury fury<br />\n<br />\nReal Madrid and Spain defender Sergio Ramos isn&rsquo;t going to make any more friends with these comments.<br />\n<br />\nThe captain of Real Madrid &mdash; who won his third-straight UEFA Champions League title and fourth in his last five years against Liverpool less than 10 days ago &mdash; has been speaking about the incidents which saw him pull Mohamed Salah to the ground and injure the left shoulder of the Egyptian winger, as well as being accused of concussing goalkeeper Loris Karius with an off-the-ball barge.<br />\n<br />\nRamos, via Spanish outlet AS, revealed he has been in touch with Salah and has sent him a message and that everything was fine on that score.<br />\n<br />\nHe then launched into the following&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;Bloody hell, they&rsquo;ve given this a lot of attention, the Salah thing&hellip;&rdquo; Ramos said. &ldquo;I didn&rsquo;t want to speak because everything is magnified. I see the play well, he grabs my arm first and I fell to the other side, the injury happened to the other arm and they said that I gave him a judo hold. After the goalkeeper said that I dazed him with a clash with me I am only missing Firmino saying that he got a cold because a drop of my sweat.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I spoke with Salah through messages, he was quite good. He could have played if he had an injection for the second half. I have done it sometimes. But when Ramos does something like this, it sticks a little bit more. I don&rsquo;t know if it&rsquo;s because you&rsquo;re at Madrid for so long and win for so long that people look at it in a different way.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"2f0da58d739a08ac0844af0adba37c0f3bd24713","tid":691252,"uid":187916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d1b71d86bbf8792fd91247cdccd79a81da3e7a","tid":691252,"uid":38189,"like":62,"dislike":7,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈呢條友已經超越丹巴巴亞成為利迷第一公敵"},{"pid":"e6fd902519f42a9db696652af61890aa4f40c3d0","tid":691252,"uid":5649,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"72d1b71d86bbf8792fd91247cdccd79a81da3e7a","tid":691252,"uid":38189,"like":62,"dislike":7,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈呢條友已經超越丹巴巴亞成為利迷第一公敵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"1.拉莫斯<br />\n2.巴亞<br />\n3.林美拉"},{"pid":"d20beaf281b8763e4f9629396826a37edff9277d","tid":691252,"uid":38189,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e6fd902519f42a9db696652af61890aa4f40c3d0","tid":691252,"uid":5649,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"72d1